Hello my friends!! 🥰 My books are currently closed to new clients, but will reopen on Saturday Nov 18! At that time y’all will be able to schedule for January 2024 ✂️

For my return clients - I have just a fewwww appointments left for this year! Click book now in my bio to grab your spot!! They won’t last long 🦋

✨ I’m still offering 30 min sessions for my return clients & I save time each week to book these. Email me to set one up, and just reach out a week or two before you’re ready to come in!

💕 and finally - if you’re a client of mine who can’t find time with me, pleaseeee book with one of the stylists on my team! You would schedule a return client session with them, you don’t need to book for 2 hours! 

🔸Check out their work here:🔸
@_twisted_scissors_ Sara Ashlee ($130/hr)
@_theintentionalstylist Sarah B ($110/hr)
@electric_expression Anna ($100/hr)

Each of these cutting specialists have been trained by me and know my tips/tricks! 🙌 You’ll be in great hands with any of them!

Thank you thank you thank you for keeping me so busy 🥹😭 I love y’all so much and I’m grateful for every single one of you that trusts me with your hairs 🥲 I have the greatest job in the world because of y’all 💞
